Technologies and frameworks:

Java 10 by default (although lombok is not compatible with Java modules yet so I was not able to utilise the modules feature) but can be converted to Java 8 by change the Java version is build.gradle
Spring Cloud
Social Login
Oauth2
Lombok
Docker
Spock (for testing)


Build the application using:

./gradlew clean build

Run the application using:

docker-compose up (on the root directory)

then:

./gradlew bootRun

It will run on port 8080

Swagger endpoint:

Currently not working
